response.original_title: Airbourne - Live at the Wacken Open Air
response.overview: AIRBOURNE - LIVE AT WACKEN on Aug. 5th 2011! I Got The Artwork from a DVD Cover Someone Made and Again Hacked It Just a Little... NOTE: Again ALL Original Credits Were Left Intact! Hi-Energy Rock & Roll Style Show... Just 9 Songs, But DAMN They Rock HARD! They Get The Crowd a-goin', And I Bet It'll Get You To Raise Your Fist In The Air, Too! Great Guitar-Driven Songs in That Familiar Australian Hard Boogie Rock N Roll Style! They Learned Their Lessons From The Masters, But Yet Add a Little Something Of Their Own to the Mix! CRANK This One LOUD!
